Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Malita Agri-Business and Marine and Aquatic School of Technology to Southern Philippines Agri-Business and Marine and Aquatic School of Technology
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 651
An Act Changing the Name of the Malita Agri-Business and Marine and Aquatic School of Technology to Southern Philippines Agri-Business and Marine and Aquatic School of Technology
Section 1. The name of the Malita Agri-Business and Marine and Aquatic School of Technology in the Municipality of Manila, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Southern Philippines Agri-Business and Marine and Aquatic School of Technology.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
